	"system":{
		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>The original masters penned this tome with the intent that it be read in a time of dire need. It holds the secret of how to use the power of the dying as a weapon against the living.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Implement</b><b>:</b> Ki focus</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Critical:</b> +3d10 necrotic critical damage</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Property:</b></p> <p>Any attack you make with this implement against a target granting combat advantage to you deals extra necrotic damage to that target. The damage equals this item's enhancement bonus.</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Daily (No Action)</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> You use assassin's strike on a bloodied target.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> The damage from assassin's strike is maximized.</p><p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Encounter (Free Action)</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> You reduce a creature adjacent to you to 0 hit points with an attack using this implement.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> You are insubstantial and phasing until the end of your next turn.</p><p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Daily (Minor Action)</b></p><p><i>Effect:</i> Your next attack this turn is made against the target's lowest defense.</p>",
